<section _ngcontent-ng-c2137494533="" class="banner justify-content-center row ng-star-inserted" style="width: 100%;"><mat-card _ngcontent-ng-c2137494533="" appearance="outlined" class="mat-mdc-card mdc-card bordered-div notice col-lg-11 col-md-11 col-sm-11 col-11 mat-mdc-card-outlined mdc-card--outlined" style="margin: 1.6em 0em;"><mat-card-title _ngcontent-ng-c2137494533="" class="mat-mdc-card-title header"> National Reserve/Complementary Income Support for Young Farmers </mat-card-title><hr _ngcontent-ng-c2137494533=""><article _ngcontent-ng-c2137494533=""><mat-card-title _ngcontent-ng-c2137494533="" class="mat-mdc-card-title header" style="text-decoration: underline;"> Important information </mat-card-title><p _ngcontent-ng-c2137494533=""> Before starting the application, please review the <a _ngcontent-ng-c2137494533="" target="_blank" href="https://www.gov.ie/en/service/bb30b-national-reserve-young-farmer-category/#faqs-and-other-support-documents">National Reserve Terms and Conditions</a> / <a _ngcontent-ng-c2137494533="" target="_blank" href="https://www.gov.ie/en/service/38d46-complementary-income-support-for-young-farmers/#faqs-and-other-support-documents">Complementary Income Support for Young Farmers Terms and Conditions</a> and also the <a _ngcontent-ng-c2137494533="" target="_blank" href="https://www.gov.ie/en/service/bb30b-national-reserve-young-farmer-category/#faqs-and-other-support-documents">National Reserve Frequently Asked Questions </a> / <a _ngcontent-ng-c2137494533="" target="_blank" href="https://www.gov.ie/en/service/38d46-complementary-income-support-for-young-farmers/#faqs-and-other-support-documents">Complementary Income Support for Young Farmers Frequently Asked Questions</a> that relate to these schemes. The closing date for applications under the 2026 National Reserve and Complementary Income Support for Young Farmers Scheme is <span _ngcontent-ng-c2137494533="" style="color: red; text-decoration: underline; font-weight: bold;">15 May 2026</span>. </p></article><p _ngcontent-ng-c2137494533="" class="ng-star-inserted">The closing date for the submission of 2026 National Reserve/Complementary Income Support for Young Farmers Scheme has now passed. </p><p _ngcontent-ng-c2137494533="" style="color: red;" class="ng-star-inserted">You may continue to submit a 2026 National Reserve/Complementary Income Support for Young Farmers application, however you must also submit supporting documentation outlining reasons for the Late Submission. </p><!----><!----></mat-card><!----></section>


