</mat-card-title><hr _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" style="margin: 1em;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" mat-dialog-content="" class="mat-mdc-dialog-content mdc-dialog__content" style="overflow: visible;"><p _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" style="text-align: left; color: black;"> Please tick the appropriate box(es) to indicate the categories you wish to apply under. Helpful information on each category can be accessed by clicking the <mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" role="img" class="mat-icon notranslate icon material-icons mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font">info</mat-icon> icons below. Applicants who meet the definition of a 'Young Farmer' are eligible to apply under both 'A. National Reserve (as Young Farmer)' and 'C. Complementary Income Support for Young Farmers'. </p></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" class="pt-3" style="margin: 0px 20px;"><form _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" novalidate="" class="ng-dirty ng-valid ng-touched"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" class="center-vertically"><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" role="img" class="mat-icon notranslate icon material-icons mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font">info</mat-icon><mat-checkbox _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" formcontrolname="nrYoungFarmer" class="mat-mdc-checkbox mat-accent ng-valid mat-mdc-checkbox-checked ng-dirty ng-untouched" id="mat-mdc-checkbox-1"><div mat-internal-form-field="" class="mdc-form-field mat-internal-form-field"><div class="mdc-checkbox"><div class="mat-mdc-checkbox-touch-target"></div><input type="checkbox" class="mdc-checkbox__native-control mdc-checkbox--selected" id="mat-mdc-checkbox-1-input" tabindex="0"><div class="mdc-checkbox__ripple"></div><div class="mdc-checkbox__background"><svg focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" class="mdc-checkbox__checkmark"><path fill="none" d="M1.73,12.91 8.1,19.28 22.79,4.59" class="mdc-checkbox__checkmark-path"></path></svg><div class="mdc-checkbox__mixedmark"></div></div><div mat-ripple="" class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-checkbox-ripple mat-mdc-focus-indicator"></div></div><label class="mdc-label" for="mat-mdc-checkbox-1-input"> A. National Reserve (as Young Farmer) </label></div></mat-checkbox></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" class="info-categories ng-star-inserted" style="text-align: left;"><p _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607=""> A young farmer applying to the National Reserve under the 2026 scheme year must be aged no more than 40 at any time in the calendar year in which they first submit an application under the National Reserve and must participate in the Basic Income Support for Sustainability Scheme in 2026. S/he must also be setting up an agricultural holding for the first time or has set up such a holding during the five years preceding this first submission of a National Reserve application. See <a _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" target="_blank" href="https://www.gov.ie/en/service/bb30b-national-reserve-young-farmer-category/"> National Reserve Terms and Conditions</a> and <a _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" target="_blank" href="https://www.gov.ie/en/service/38d46-complementary-income-support-for-young-farmers/">Complementary Income Support for Young Farmers Scheme Terms and Conditions</a> for the full definition of a 'Young Farmer'. </p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607=""> A person who meets the definition of a 'young farmer' may be eligible to apply under Categories A (National Reserve as Young Farmer) and C (Complementary Income Support for Young Farmers). </p></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" class="center-vertically"><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" role="img" class="mat-icon notranslate icon material-icons mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font">info</mat-icon><mat-checkbox _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" formcontrolname="nrNewFarmer" class="mat-mdc-checkbox mat-accent ng-valid ng-dirty ng-touched" id="mat-mdc-checkbox-2"><div mat-internal-form-field="" class="mdc-form-field mat-internal-form-field"><div class="mdc-checkbox"><div class="mat-mdc-checkbox-touch-target"></div><input type="checkbox" class="mdc-checkbox__native-control" id="mat-mdc-checkbox-2-input" tabindex="0"><div class="mdc-checkbox__ripple"></div><div class="mdc-checkbox__background"><svg focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" class="mdc-checkbox__checkmark"><path fill="none" d="M1.73,12.91 8.1,19.28 22.79,4.59" class="mdc-checkbox__checkmark-path"></path></svg><div class="mdc-checkbox__mixedmark"></div></div><div mat-ripple="" class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-checkbox-ripple mat-mdc-focus-indicator"></div></div><label class="mdc-label" for="mat-mdc-checkbox-2-input"> B. National Reserve (as New Farmer) </label></div></mat-checkbox></div><mat-error _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" aria-atomic="true" class="mat-mdc-form-field-error mat-mdc-form-field-bottom-align ng-star-inserted" aria-live="polite" id="mat-mdc-error-1"> You may not select 'B. National Reserve (as New Farmer)' with 'A. National Reserve (as Young Farmer)'. Please uncheck category A before selecting this. </mat-error><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" class="info-categories ng-star-inserted" style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0.5em;"><p _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607=""> A 'new farmer' applying to the National Reserve under the 2026 scheme year must have commenced his/her present agricultural activity in the 2023 calendar year or later. Applicants under this category must participate in the Basic Income Support for Sustainability Scheme in 2026. See the <a _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" target="_blank" href="https://www.gov.ie/en/service/5b7788-national-reserve-new-entrant-category/"> National Reserve Terms and Conditions</a> for the full definition of a 'New Farmer'. </p><p _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607=""> While no age restrictions is applied to a 'new farmer', persons who apply under this category will normally be aged over 40 in the year they apply to the National Reserve. It is therefore unlikely that a person who applies under Category B(New Farmer) would be eligible on age grounds to apply under Category A(National Reserve as a Young Farmer). </p></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" class="center-vertically"><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" role="img" class="mat-icon notranslate icon material-icons mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font">info</mat-icon><mat-checkbox _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" formcontrolname="nrCisyf" class="mat-mdc-checkbox mat-accent ng-valid ng-dirty ng-untouched" id="mat-mdc-checkbox-3"><div mat-internal-form-field="" class="mdc-form-field mat-internal-form-field"><div class="mdc-checkbox"><div class="mat-mdc-checkbox-touch-target"></div><input type="checkbox" class="mdc-checkbox__native-control" id="mat-mdc-checkbox-3-input" tabindex="0"><div class="mdc-checkbox__ripple"></div><div class="mdc-checkbox__background"><svg focusable="false" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" class="mdc-checkbox__checkmark"><path fill="none" d="M1.73,12.91 8.1,19.28 22.79,4.59" class="mdc-checkbox__checkmark-path"></path></svg><div class="mdc-checkbox__mixedmark"></div></div><div mat-ripple="" class="mat-ripple mat-mdc-checkbox-ripple mat-mdc-focus-indicator"></div></div><label class="mdc-label" for="mat-mdc-checkbox-3-input"> C. Complementary income Support for Young Farmers </label></div></mat-checkbox></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" class="info-categories ng-star-inserted" style="text-align: left;"><p _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607=""> If the applicant meets the definition of a 'Young Farmer' they may be eligible to apply under category <b _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="">'C. Complementary Income Support for Young Farmers'</b> along with the National Reserve. Please see the <a _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" target="_blank" style="color: #e4d094;" href="https://www.gov.ie/en/service/38d46-complementary-income-support-for-young-farmers/">Complementary Income Support for Young Farmers Scheme Terms and Conditions</a> for the full eligibility criteria for Complementary Income Support for Young Farmers Scheme. </p></div><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" mat-dialog-actions="" align="end" class="mat-mdc-dialog-actions mdc-dialog__actions mat-mdc-dialog-actions-align-end"><button _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" type="button" class="nav-button clearBtn"><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" role="img" class="mat-icon notranslate material-icons mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font">close</mat-icon><span _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="">Close</span></button><button _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" type="button" class="nav-button"><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" role="img" class="mat-icon notranslate material-icons mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" style="color: white;" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font"> navigate_next </mat-icon><span _ngcontent-ng-c3068956607="" style="color: white;"> Next </span></button></div></form></div><!----></app-nr-cisyf-category-select-popup><!----></div></div></mat-dialog-container><div tabindex="0" class="cdk-visually-hidden cdk-focus-trap-anchor" aria-hidden="true"></div></div>


